Introduction to Assembly (RISC-V)
- CI1210 - Universidade Federal do Paraná
(Federal University of Paraná)
Arithmetic and Logic Instructions

Operate on registers:
add, sub
xor, or, and
sll, srl, sra
slt, sltu

Examples:
add t1, t2, t3
sub t1, t1, t2
xor t1, t1, t1

With immediate:
addi,
xori, ori, andi
slli, srli, srai
slti, sltiu

Examples:
addi t1, zero, 42
slli t2, t1, 2
andi t1, t1, 0xff

Multiplication Extension:
mul, mulh, mulsu, mulu
div, divu
rem, remu

Examples:
Load immediate: addi t1, zero, imm
Copy value: addi t1, t2, 0

Immediates are only 12 bits long!
